          â€¢ Updated property valuations<br/>
          â€¢ Owner contact information updates<br/>
          â€¢ Investment opportunity status changes
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding-bottom="30px" padding-top="0px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-button background-color="#2563eb" color="#ffffff" font-size="16px" font-weight="bold" href="https://app.crefinder.ai/dashboard" padding="15px 30px" border-radius="6px">
          View Updated Properties
        </mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#f0f9ff" padding="20px" border-radius="8px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text align="center" color="#1e40af" font-size="16px" font-weight="600" line-height="24px">
          ðŸ’¡ Pro Tip
